OL,4,CEndometriosis: Bride-to-be 'pleading'
OL,5,Cfor hysterectomy aged 23
OL,6, A 23-year-old woman who begged doctors
OL,7, to remove her womb to relieve chronic
OL,8, pain says the surgery is being refused
OL,9, due to her age and childless status.
OL,11,FHannah Lockhart has endometriosis, a
OL,12,Fcondition that can cause debilitating
OL,13,Fpain, heavy periods and infertility.
OL,15,FAlthough she has always wanted her own
OL,16,Fchildren, Hannah says her daily pain is
OL,17,Fnow so severe she wants a hysterectomy.
OL,19,F"It's heartbreaking that just because
OL,20,FI'm so young I have to keep suffering,"
OL,21,Fshe told the BBC's Evening Extra show.
